<span class='communityAnswerText'>
<span class="expandableContainer"><span class="truncatedContent">I read it to my 6 year old and she loves it. I did, however, skip over or adjust sections I felt she would be too sensitive to. Or, rather, rephrase t<a class="jsShow showAction" href="#">…more</a></span><span class="fullContent">I read it to my 6 year old and she loves it. I did, however, skip over or adjust sections I felt she would be too sensitive to. Or, rather, rephrase them so she could still hear about them but in a manner more suitable to her age. She said the best thing is that this book has no pictures so she can imagine instead.<a class="jsHide hideAction" href="#">(less)</a></span></span>
