          <div><span class="uitext greyText">Recommends it for: </span>
           <span class="uitext reviewText">everyone who's ever suffered from escapism | всеки, страдащ/-л от ескейпизъм</span></div>

        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/741149-kalin?shelf=reviewed-in-english">reviewed-in-english</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/741149-kalin?shelf=uplifting">uplifting</a>
